      "text": [
        "2337 - وَ قَالَ لَهُ زَيْدٌ اَلشَّحَّامُ : أُخْرِجُ مِنَ اَلْمَسْجِدِ حَصَاةً قَالَ «فَرُدَّهَا أَوِ اِطْرَحْهَا فِي مَسْجِدٍ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2337 - Zayd Al-Shahham said to him (Abu Abdullah (as)):\n\"May I take a pebble out of the mosque?\"\nImam (as) replied: \"Return it or place it in another mosque.\""
        ]
      }
    }
